des:
This voice app walks users through the services of MML Therapy. At MML Physical Therapy in Las Vegas you will find a different approach to healing. Our team is dedicated to ensuring a better life for all our patients. The unique, fun environment that we have created invites you be a part of our family as we work together to meet your needs.

We have been serving the Las Vegas valley since 1992 and we are one of the only privately owned physical therapy practices in town.
